Dear <%= @order.customer.name %>,
<br><br>
We are writing to inform you of a status update on your recent order with us.
<br><br>
Order Details<br>
=============<br>
Order ID: <%= @order.id %><br>
Current Status: <%= @order.status %><br>
Total Price: $<%= sprintf('%.2f', @order.total_price) %>
<br><br>
Your order was placed at: <%= @order.created_at.strftime('%I:%M%p %Z on %B %d, %Y') %>
<%if @order.status == "Picked Up"%>
    <br>Order picked up at: <%= @order.end_time.strftime('%I:%M%p %Z on %B %d, %Y') %>
<%end%>
<br><br>
Order Items<br>
===========<br>
<% @order.order_items.each do |item| %>
- Item Name: <%= item.menu_item.name %><br>
  Quantity: <%= item.quantity %><br>
  Price: $<%= sprintf('%.2f', item.menu_item.price * item.quantity) %><br>
  <br>
<% end %>

We appreciate your patience and are working diligently to prepare your order. 
<br><br>
Thank you for choosing <%@order.restaurant.name%>! We hope to serve you again soon.
<br><br>
Warm regards,<br>
The Team at [The silly geese]<br>